{"tid":1614143,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"藍絲同中資的確需要懲治","createTime":"2019-10-02T16:57:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T02:06:53.000Z","uid":210285,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0aca0d39274f41a75a5ac9a31702eeff6bf70b4f","tid":1614143,"uid":210285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T16:57:34.000Z","msg":"我知道民意已經歸邊<br />\n但係唔好唔記得<strong>同溫層效應</strong><br />\n一個運動唔單單需要連登嘅支持<br />\n要走得更耐更遠係需要大家嘅理解<br />\n唔係話驚民意逆轉<br />\n只係我地仲有咁多目標<br />\n例如民建聯、正苦建築、（當然仲有黨鐵）<br />\n係咪可以諗下緩急輕重/目標呢<br />\n當然唔代表要停藍絲黑商呢條戰線<br />\n只係唔想佢成為主線<br />\n求集思廣益<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申 睇藍絲舖頭被跪低真係好爽<br />\n感謝勇武前線付出<br />\n但係文宣都真係要跟返上<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多老一輩都唔太明白<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但我懇請你們不要被仇恨支配自己，在危難中，仍要時刻保持警覺與思考</span></span></strong>。"},{"pid":"8328496812f152c90e9fcd4d62134e5fcd91ef37","tid":1614143,"uid":210285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T16:59:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aba7e58f4b4eb6d4b9fbf746c0b3ea58955ac1e1","tid":1614143,"uid":210285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T17:01:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e1ef61112e32b7bcb91aecc4ea451ad04e4d7a6","tid":1614143,"uid":210285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T17:05:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cf53a94dd7def65edbad48d6e5adb3a750c6bc0","tid":1614143,"uid":220690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T17:07:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5f02d82bf14e1c0060cf2d21e54f4dbc57884967","tid":16141